menu "PixelPet"

    config PIXELPET_TIME_SCALE
        int "Game-time scale factor"
        range 1 3600
        default 120
        help
            Multiplier between real seconds and game seconds. With the
            default of 120, one real minute equals two game hours, so:
              EGG → BABY    in ~15 real-min
              BABY → CHILD  in   3 real-min after that
              TEEN → ADULT  in  36 real-min after that
              ADULT → SENIOR in 84 real-min after that
            The full lifecycle is ~2.5 real-hours — long enough to feel
            like a pet, short enough for an evening playtest. Set to 1
            for true real-time play (one game-day = one real-day) or to
            360 for fast iteration (lifecycle in ~30 real-min).

endmenu
